{"type": "article", "id": 24560, "title": "想要在春天扮复古？这里有 4 种眼镜可供选择", "description": "特点是面积都够大。", "date": "2016-03-28T16:10:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153913viDxmZPFKeY57pBt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">前些年，当眼镜都还长得小巧玲珑时，戴框架眼镜不太能加分。后来，眼镜的面积越长越大，换句话说，长回了上个世纪 70 、80 年代的样子时，戴眼镜就变成了日常凹造型的一个杀手锏。</p>\n<p class=\"\">最近流行的眼镜大部分镜框都比较大，但是看起来也更衬脸型，有一种轻松的造型感。除了玳瑁的材质之外，透明的眼镜框也开始流行起来，是扮复古的一个新选择。</p>\n<h2>1.透明眼镜框</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153905oli7KgtJ4fSjHn8E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153905VLtlExCji4cU8uno.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.15384615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153906V2T6cJso0WjOqvdR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53191489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153906xLtGwKlAEdZNQWSY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45918367\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153907md2JiEH0LkCD3oPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">透明材质的眼镜框流行了一段时间。和前两年那种无边框眼镜比起来，全透明材质的镜框虽然看起来是在强调“看不见边框”，不过，醉翁之意却是要让人时不时看到这两个透明的圆圈。而且，这种全透明的镜框也很适合面若桃花（抹了大红唇）的脸。</p>\n<h2>2.70 年代感金属镜框</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153907sPneJMKHFN7yGOCl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153908fjhqZr9HlF4gWYkC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153908scYueBEIAQSdGzLU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153908dwp9PhcCzensqoIS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50377834\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>如果你一直是近视眼，估计读小学的时候有戴过这种金属质地的镜框。不过，当时的审美还停留在眼镜框覆盖住眼睛的阶段，镜框长得相当小巧。但现在，金丝眼镜了越长越大了。在 2016 年 Gucci  的 T 台 ，这种放大版的金丝眼镜很抢眼，配上一根眼镜链就名正言顺地复古了。</p>\n<h2>3.方方圆圆的镜框</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153909Ht7S5JMiKZOnyGfB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153909cfQATLbrsZRBNoYu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061539107dvCo8EhWKOTfqLi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153911VLpG1gNc06W7RXh4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87288136\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153911Wrhmq9bF30vLMsTd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">方方圆圆的眼镜框一直挺流行，特别是玳瑁或者仿玳瑁的颜色更是很走俏。不过接下来，一些颜色更大胆的镜框可能会更吸引人。</p>\n<h2>4.蝴蝶型镜框</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153911iR3qPMAHEIvQcmk1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153912yCoBLPnkIVbYSM7N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18644068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061539138nUSitzBjJCqHmog.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">蝴蝶型镜框比较特别，有一种古灵精怪的气质。不过也更挑人，一不小心就会复古过了头，真的变成了“古”。总得来说，这是一种“如果没什么必要那就不要试了吧”的款。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">题图和文内图来自：<a href=\"http://www.luxuryeyewearforum.com/category/frame/page/3/\">luxuryeyewearforum</a>、<a href=\"http://us.shadestation.com/media/thumbs/350x218.75/media/product_images/Oliver-Peoples-Glasses-OV1190-5244-46-sidefw350fh218.75.jpg\">us.shadestation</a><a href=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/236x/41/6b/00/416b007170649eae23423c66c8edf8ae.jpg\">、</a><a href=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/236x/7d/68/1f/7d681f5b21bc34feca7068316a9c936b.jpg\">s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg</a>、<a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/572942383816135274/\">pinterest</a>、<a href=\"http://www.ebay.com.sg/itm/80s-Retro-Classic-Aviator-Gradient-Frame-Clear-Lenses-Men-Women-Uni-Eyeglasses-/321243734895\">ebay</a>、<a href=\"http://www.selectspecs.com/fashion-lifestyle/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Gucci-eyewear-for-2016.jpg\">selectspecs</a>、<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/3/26/11302026/glasses-eyewear-trend-shop\">racked</a></p>\n\n\n"}